{"id": "bede.sample.0001", "src": "oe_bede_sample", "work": "Bede (Old English) — SAMPLE", "loc": "sample:1", "srcp": "sample:1", "lang": "ang", "txt": "Ða was micel storm on sæ, and þa scipu hæfdon earfoðnysse; se lareow bæd for sibbe and stillnesse.", "sha256": "629fff52042d56b774bd3978e6c3af0f47b6e8ef0c4e88560604be9bcd235668"}
{"id": "bede.sample.0002", "src": "oe_bede_sample", "work": "Bede (Old English) — SAMPLE", "loc": "sample:2", "srcp": "sample:2", "lang": "ang", "txt": "Se biscop spræc be fulluhte and synna forgyfenesse; he nemde þæt man sceal on life beon soðfæst.", "sha256": "a55fd9bfd5dc6a3c0b4884357e250a505bc043f65249b440fa4c7545e16ef34f"}
{"id": "bede.sample.0003", "src": "oe_bede_sample", "work": "Bede (Old English) — SAMPLE", "loc": "sample:3", "srcp": "sample:3", "lang": "ang", "txt": "Þæt folc gaderode to cyrcan; þær wæs ræd and lar, and menn gehyrdon mid eadmodnesse.", "sha256": "c9af84a7756b5873cd90add038f27c8bfc132171c2f276c87eee4b7b0375183f"}
{"id": "bede.sample.0004", "src": "oe_bede_sample", "work": "Bede (Old English) — SAMPLE", "loc": "sample:4", "srcp": "sample:4", "lang": "ang", "txt": "Ne mæg nan man beon ana strong; forþon is freondscipe and anrædnes þurh Godes gife.", "sha256": "50b89a93badef0952900cc00a8549b97b70641d9b7ec3e340f4e11c5e1c34b0d"}
{"id": "bede.sample.0005", "src": "oe_bede_sample", "work": "Bede (Old English) — SAMPLE", "loc": "sample:5", "srcp": "sample:5", "lang": "ang", "txt": "Sume men cwædon þæt he wære geleafful; oðre tweodon. Her is þearf þæt we sette [ ] þær we ne witon.", "sha256": "4c6f6a3e221c9a78f4260052c2e4863341cd029319f2ac940c27d1f13863a477"}
{"id": "bede.sample.0006", "src": "oe_bede_sample", "work": "Bede (Old English) — SAMPLE", "loc": "sample:6", "srcp": "sample:6", "lang": "ang", "txt": "Se munuc awrat on bocfelle; he heold endebyrdnesse on wordum and setnysse on stafum.", "sha256": "2a395dbd5a82b861789ca20d8b54b51a6f7ef0782d4803eb0f89ebfd235d4519"}
{"id": "bede.sample.0007", "src": "oe_bede_sample", "work": "Bede (Old English) — SAMPLE", "loc": "sample:7", "srcp": "sample:7", "lang": "ang", "txt": "Þa sæde se læce þæt lufu is bindend; hit læt þa heortan beon gehælede fram hatheortnesse.", "sha256": "5357eac8e30e984a132b9e5d106cb7fb459b05bd1ed8cbd076c65667497c6a4c"}
{"id": "bede.sample.0008", "src": "oe_bede_sample", "work": "Bede (Old English) — SAMPLE", "loc": "sample:8", "srcp": "sample:8", "lang": "ang", "txt": "On þære tid wæs fæsten and gebed; men sæton stille and smeadon hu hi bettere wæron.", "sha256": "925a5555079bede2bbb423fe46a44dd0eab68f9e064167aea3357f24443ffa00"}
{"id": "bede.sample.0009", "src": "oe_bede_sample", "work": "Bede (Old English) — SAMPLE", "loc": "sample:9", "srcp": "sample:9", "lang": "ang", "txt": "Swa swa leoht oftor scinð, swa sceal wisdom oftor beon on larum; ac we sceolan wærlice spræcan.", "sha256": "7614da7c984c87a4ed9e386b3719b41032fd9352eaa0e62517e8e95bb5b792ff"}
{"id": "bede.sample.0010", "src": "oe_bede_sample", "work": "Bede (Old English) — SAMPLE", "loc": "sample:10", "srcp": "sample:10", "lang": "ang", "txt": "Þær wæs gemynd of ealdum tidum; þa lareowas hæfdon gewuna to rædan and to writanne mid getreownesse.", "sha256": "c8b30cf9fb0f81889f1a5e39d00d912791adffa1464cd52a47c2c4d64f68bfe5"}
{"id": "bede.sample.0011", "src": "oe_bede_sample", "work": "Bede (Old English) — SAMPLE", "loc": "sample:11", "srcp": "sample:11", "lang": "ang", "txt": "Ne is hit æfre alyfed to awendan þa boc butan andgit; forþon we healdan þisne text swa hit is.", "sha256": "08ac9026c2ab0ba65b2f15985201e5b9f846ae3fbce05aee7eab58542c1065c5"}
{"id": "bede.sample.0012", "src": "oe_bede_sample", "work": "Bede (Old English) — SAMPLE", "loc": "sample:12", "srcp": "sample:12", "lang": "ang", "txt": "Her endað þæt sample; hit is na soð Beda text, ac an lytel demo to cyðan þa formate.", "sha256": "e9c704360ae581127e2d6cf4eaae3bd2f1e44241b8b016c73da43520b29e29fd"}
